summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed of conveyance from Chicago, Milwaukee & St. Paul Railway Company of Washington to The City of Seattle of a strip of land one hundred (100) feet in width and eight hundred and six and one-tenth (806.1) feet in length, the same being all of lot six (6) and the north forty (40) feet of lot seven (7) in block three hundred seventy-three (373), Seattle Tide Lands.
